: Offentlege fridagar
"1. Nyttårsdag" weekend on 1.1
"2. Nyttårsdag" on 2.1
"Grunnlovsdag" weekend on 17.5

: Andre merkedagar
"Morsdag" on second sunday in february
"Sommertid" on last sunday in march
"Vintertid" on last sunday in september
"Farsdag" on second sunday in november
"Nyttårsaften" on 31 december
"Kvinnedagen" on 8 march

: Offentlege fridagar frå kristen tradisjon 
"Bots & bededag" weekend on last sunday in october
"Søn. før faste" weekend on easter minus 49
"Skjærtorsdag" weekend on easter minus 3
"Langfredag" weekend on easter minus 2
"Påskeaften" on easter minus 1
"1. Påskedag" weekend on easter
"2. Påskedag" weekend on easter plus 1
"Pinseaften" on easter plus 48 days
"1. Pinsedag" weekend on easter plus 49 days
"2. Pinsedag" weekend on easter plus 50 days
"Kristi Him.f.dag" weekend on easter plus 39 days
"Off. høytidsdag" weekend on 1.5
"1. Juledag" weekend on 25.12
"2. Juledag" weekend on 26.12

: Andre vanlege merkedagar frå kristen tradisjon
"St. Hans" on 23.6
"1. Advent" on sunday before 23.12 minus 21 days
"2. Advent" on sunday before 23.12 minus 14 days
"3. Advent" on sunday before 23.12 minus 7 days
"4. Advent" on sunday before 23.12
"Julaften" on 24.12
